# Adopt-a-pet Assignment

Adopt-a-pet tasks: (do 3 in total):
Book an apppointment (required!)
to make is simple, simply print the hours of operation and have the user select a Day of the week - write that into the User class
you will need to add that property to the User class
fix/improve all PRINT statements! (with color as well, research)
add a validation method for the Book an appointment method/option/feature
complete the Form class:
add a Form with 3 fields to the Form class (applicantName, address, phone number)
add a fillForm method to the Form class
add a printForm method to the Main driver class
make sure you can goBack to the main menu from the book an appointment option
please add a readme in the Repo detailing which tasks you completed!
